title: Local non-profit seeks to hire a Regional Director for
text:
Local non-profit seeks to hire a Regional Director for ad date: 10/17/2015 
Local non-profit seeks to hire a Regional Director for Outpatient Mental Health Clinic. Minimum qualifications possess; CA Licensed Marriage family therapist or CA Licensed Clinical Social Worker. Full-time/benefits/salary. Duties include: Oversight of Staff and daily operations and networking with partner agencies. Must pass background check/drug screen. Please send resume to bbohannon@remivistainc.org
